You will have Queen sized bed with linen, 40inch LED TV with cable channels, Air conditioner, wall fan, Hair dryer, Towels changed daily, Sofa Bed with coffee table. You can enjoy Wifi, and House keeping service. 2 Washing machines are also available for your use just outside the apartment. Smoking is strictly disallowed inside the apartment.
My place is located in Kembangan, East Coast of Singapore. You can expect a peaceful,tranquil and beautiful atmosphere in my place. I pride myself in providing only clean, comfortable and private stay for all my guest.
1min walking distance to a bus stop there are many buses to major attractions and the city centre. 3~4mins to Kembangan MRT station. By foot, you can reach eateries and shops in 4mins. And there are lots of nice local restaurants, 24hr Convenience store just behind the house!
25mins travel time to Raffles Place and Tanjong Pagar.
My house is near Geylang which is the old red light district; there are lots of famous restaurants and you can buy Durians! There are many shops only selling durians at the nearby Katong area.
East coast park which is the biggest beach in Singapore is 5 mins drive away. At East Coast Park ( Which is about 30mins by foot using the park connector) there are many nice restaurants and a big food court where u can try various kinds of south East Asian food.

This spacious studio apartment has a floor space of about 700 sq ft. It comes with own private entrance, attached bathroom, own kitchen with microwave, bread toaster & full sized fridge. Outside the apartment, there is even a seating place for smoking or your visiting guests.
You will have Queen sized bed with linen, 40inch LED TV with cable channels, Air conditioner, wall fan, Hair dryer, Towels changed daily, Sofa Bed with coffee table. You can enjoy Wifi, and House keeping service. 2 Washing machines are also available for your use just outside the apartment. Smoking is strictly disallowed inside the apartment.
My place is located in Kembangan, East Coast of Singapore. You can expect a peaceful,tranquil and beautiful atmosphere in my place. I pride myself in providing only clean, comfortable and private stay for all my guest.
1min walking distance to a bus stop there are many buses to major attractions and the city centre. 3~4mins to Kembangan MRT station. By foot, you can reach eateries and shops in 4mins. And there are lots of nice local restaurants, 24hr Convenience store just behind the house!
25mins travel time to Raffles Place and Tanjong Pagar.
My house is near Geylang which is the old red light district; there are lots of famous restaurants and you can buy Durians! There are many shops only selling durians at the nearby Katong area.
East coast park which is the biggest beach in Singapore is 5 mins drive away. At East Coast Park ( Which is about 30mins by foot using the park connector) there are many nice restaurants and a big food court where u can try various kinds of south East Asian food.

The apartment is located in Novena, which is a great place to be if you want to be close to city centre. It is also a popular choice for medical tourist because it is not more than 15 min away from many hospitals and medical centres, like Thomson Medical Centre, Gleneagles, Mount Elizabeth Hospital etc. The apartment is a 3 minutes walk to the Novena MRT. You will have Queen sized bed with linen, 40inch LED TV with cable channels, Air conditioner, wall fan, Hair dryer, Towels changed daily, Sofa Bed with coffee table. You can enjoy Wifi, and House keeping service. 2 Washing machines are also available for your use just outside the apartment. Smoking is strictly disallowed inside the apartment.
My place is located in Kembangan, East Coast of Singapore. You can expect a peaceful,tranquil and beautiful atmosphere in my place. I pride myself in providing only clean, comfortable and private stay for all my guest.
1min walking distance to a bus stop there are many buses to major attractions and the city centre. 3~4mins to Kembangan MRT station. By foot, you can reach eateries and shops in 4mins. And there are lots of nice local restaurants, 24hr Convenience store just behind the house!
25mins travel time to Raffles Place and Tanjong Pagar.
My house is near Geylang which is the old red light district; there are lots of famous restaurants and you can buy Durians! There are many shops only selling durians at the nearby Katong area.
East coast park which is the biggest beach in Singapore is 5 mins drive away. At East Coast Park ( Which is about 30mins by foot using the park connector) there are many nice restaurants and a big food court where u can try various kinds of south East Asian food.
